OL,7,FParcel firms have delivered a
OL,8,F"miserable" service to consumers for
OL,9,Fthe third year running, according to
OL,10,Fan annual survey by Citizens Advice.
OL,12,FEvri and Yodel ranked at the bottom
OL,13,Fof the charity's league table, both
OL,14,Fmanaging an overall score of just two
OL,15,Fstars out of a possible five.
OL,17,FHowever, none of the major parcel
OL,18,Ffirms managed to secure even a three
OL,19,Fstar rating, with Royal Mail and
OL,20,FAmazon achieving joint best position
OL,21,Fwith a meagre 2.75 stars.
